{"tid":1146891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲男子好心幫助路上女子修理壞車  遭誣告猥褻侵犯失去工作和婚姻","createTime":"2019-05-09T13:45:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T07:03:29.000Z","uid":2748,"like":527,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":98,"replies":[{"pid":"c2f0fda8b16505cc8483608240028cbf7b5388e8","tid":1146891,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T13:45:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://files.mastodon.social/media_attachments/files/014/404/704/small/a536c0c5caa82bcd.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffiles.mastodon.social%2Fmedia_attachments%2Ffiles%2F014%2F404%2F704%2Fsmall%2Fa536c0c5caa82bcd.jpeg&h=9170fba6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一位善良的悉尼男子花兩小時幫助一名年輕女性修理拋錨的車，卻遭女子誣告，指稱他對自己性侵犯，致使該名男子被關押兩星期，身心受創，丟了工作也面臨離婚危機，好在法庭判男子無罪，該女子則面臨刑責。<br />\n<br />\n據9號電視台報導，一位善良的悉尼男子花兩小時幫助一名年輕女性修理拋錨的車，卻遭女子誣告，指稱他對自己性侵犯，致使該名男子被關押兩星期，身心受創，丟了工作也面臨離婚危機，好在法庭判男子無罪，該女子則面臨刑責。<br />\n<br />\n2018年11月，一名19歲的女子在悉尼西南部的Bankstown撞了車，並將車子拖到加油站後，36歲的已婚父親Kenan Basic決定停下幫助這名女子，他花了將近兩個小時幫助修車，好讓這位女子可以將她的車開迴路上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.auliving.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/the-36-year-old-married-father-of-one-spent-almost.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.auliving.com.au%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2Fthe-36-year-old-married-father-of-one-spent-almost.jpeg&h=216ab55b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據加油站的監視畫面顯示，兩人在車子前愉快地聊天，甚至擁抱。然後他跟著女子的車一小段距離，以確保她沒有再次發生問題。<br />\n<br />\n然而，在她開走後，這名女子告訴警方，Basic不雅地毆打並跟踪她，在跟隨她並再次指導她之前，Basic已經提出要發生關係以換取他的幫助。<br />\n<br />\n在對他提出虛假指控後，Basic在Silverwater監獄被監禁兩個星期，失去了工作，現在正面臨離婚危機。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.auliving.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/gray-told-police-mr-basic-pictured-had-allegedly.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.auliving.com.au%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2Fgray-told-police-mr-basic-pictured-had-allegedly.jpeg&h=b659bc37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nKenan Basic 表示：&ldquo;我這一生總是盡量幫助人，這是第一次被蛇咬。&rdquo;他說，在這名女子誣告他對她性侵犯之後，他的生活已經破滅。<br />\n<br />\n星期一，所有針對Basic的指控都被證實為不實，因為這位女子在接受采訪時，在偵探的壓力下說了實話，她的這些指控都是撒謊。<br />\n<br />\n面對審判結果，Basic 表示：&ldquo;我感到高興，因為我得到了自由。&rdquo;Basic表示，這事件使她以後不會再次停下幫助年輕女子。<br />\n<br />\n這名女子現在面臨著故意作出虛假或誤導性指控，並將於下週出庭。<br />\n<br />\n原文新聞：<br />\nGood Samaritan spends two weeks in a maximum security prison after woman whose car he helped fix falsely accused him of indecent assault<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-6996829/Good-Samaritan-says-woman-accused-assaulting-fixing-car-up.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-6996829%2FGood-Samaritan-says-woman-accused-assaulting-fixing-car-up.html&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYSNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=1383b2be\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-6996829/Good-Samaritan-says-woman-accused-assaulting-fixing-car-up.html</a>"},{"pid":"422ac6d3eba1a9026d52d308275ea02f504a538e","tid":1146891,"uid":143241,"like":757,"dislike":1,"score":756,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T13:46:20.000Z","msg":"佢個樣好絕望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03444ec9fa129655ac76c83d2ee0875c0698b7c0","tid":1146891,"uid":44171,"like":764,"dislike":0,"score":764,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T13:47:53.000Z","msg":"女人個樣又打格<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89bbf1a26c39c20832d62ec2a915b91c1e7d05aa","tid":1146891,"uid":2748,"like":292,"dislike":0,"score":292,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T13:48:20.000Z","msg":"'I feel happy because I got my freedom you know,' Mr Basic said.<br />\n<br />\nThe teenager is now facing a charge of knowingly making false or misleading statement and will appear in court next week.<br />\n<br />\nMr Basic said <span style=\"color: red;\">the incident has deterred him from stopping and helping a young woman ever again</span>."},{"pid":"2dfcd7b7f30ebeae32b9e8380fa75f7333c6a466","tid":1146891,"uid":164730,"like":465,"di